Text: Finally, this one is the complete version. Bravo!

You only had to watch the opening number to understand why REAL actors prefer the stage, and talentless twats (hello Paris Hilton) make movies. Couldn't the people who produce the Oscars hire some of these people so the opening number doesn't always suck? There is NOTHING like live theatre.

"It's not just for gays anymooooooore!"
There is no sound for a couple seconds during the Catch Me If You Can number.
